name: Pitaya
description:
Pitaya, also known as Dragon Fruit, is a superfruit indigenous to Central and South America that is now grown all over the world.

In 2017 I was researching dragon fruit to be the main theme for my video art project, but at that moment the project had problems in its realization. So, I decided to make another option for the artwork which is a digital painting, and here is it "Pitaya".

JPEG 1600x1600 px
